snippet.textDisplay: A lot of comments are complaining about Coke Studios’ new format and songs.  Old Coke Studios was regurgitating old songs in new presentations.  S14&15 has dared to be different.  They are making new music and at the same time engaging more senses.  They are also pushing the boundaries in professionalism, just look at set design, attention to detail, visual presentation, etc.  Why cant we accept creativity, maybe this is why we are so far behind rest of the world.  You have to break some eggs to make an omelette.
